{"body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"optionalcookie\">\n<span id=\"id1\"></span><h1>optionalCookie</h1>\n<p>Extracts an optional cookie with a given name from a request.</p>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"signature\">\n<h2>Signature</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight-scala\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">optionalCookie</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">String</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Directive1</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">Option</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">HttpCookie</span><span class=\"o\">]]</span> \n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"description\">\n<h2>Description</h2>\n<p>Use the <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../cookie/#cookie\"><em>cookie</em></a> directive instead if the inner route does not handle a missing cookie.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"example\">\n<h2>Example</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight-scala\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span class=\"k\">val</span> <span class=\"n\">route</span> <span class=\"k\">=</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">optionalCookie</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;userName&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">case</span> <span class=\"nc\">Some</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">nameCookie</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"k\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">complete</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;The logged in user is &#39;${nameCookie.content}&#39;&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">case</span> <span class=\"nc\">None</span> <span class=\"k\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">complete</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;No user logged in&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">}</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"nc\">Get</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;/&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"nc\">Cookie</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nc\">HttpCookie</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;userName&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;paul&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">))</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">route</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">check</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">responseAs</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">String</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">===</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;The logged in user is &#39;paul&#39;&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n<span class=\"nc\">Get</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;/&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">route</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">check</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">responseAs</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">String</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">===</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;No user logged in&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n", "display_toc": true, "title": "optionalCookie", "sourcename": "", "customsidebar": null, "current_page_name": "documentation/spray-routing/cookie-directives/optionalCookie", "next": {"link": "../setCookie/", "title": "setCookie"}, "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["documentation/spray-routing/cookie-directives/setCookie", "setCookie", "N", "next"], ["documentation/spray-routing/cookie-directives/deleteCookie", "deleteCookie", "P", "previous"]], "meta": {}, "parents": [{"link": "../../../", "title": "Documentation"}, {"link": "../../", "title": "spray-routing"}, {"link": "../../predefined-directives-by-trait/", "title": "Predefined Directives (by trait)"}, {"link": "../", "title": "CookieDirectives"}], "sidebars": null, "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">optionalCookie</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#signature\">Signature</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#description\">Description</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#example\">Example</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "prev": {"link": "../deleteCookie/", "title": "deleteCookie"}, "metatags": ""}